## Notes

- The Active Directory group must exist before import. The Tableau API validates group existence.
- When `async_mode` is `true`, the resource polls job status every 2 seconds for up to 2 minutes.
- If `site` is omitted, the resource uses the default site from the provider configuration.
- Site groups cannot be updated after creation. Changes require resource recreation.
- The resource creates a site-specific authenticated session for non-default sites.
- Domain name can be auto-extracted from the group name if it follows the format `domain\groupname`.
